"SpringDoc OpenAPI 2.5.0 is configured in each service via SwaggerConfig.java. JWT Bearer authentication is configured in the Swagger UI so evaluators can test protected endpoints directly from the browser without Postman. Each controller has @Tag for grouping and @Operation for endpoint descriptions. Swagger UI is accessible at /swagger-ui.html on each service port."

Logging:

